Title: "Emotional But Rational Move": Ikea Stops Print Catalogue After 70 Years
Description: Swedish furniture giant Ikea said Monday it would stop printing its famed physical catalogue, printed yearly in tens of millions of copies, after 70 years, as customers move to digital alternatives.

Title: AK Vs AK Trailer: Anil Kapoor And Anurag Kashyap's Rivalry Is As Real As It Gets. Surprise Cameo By Sonam Kapoor
Description: Anil Kapoor, not quite happy with the original trailer, also shared his "real" version of the trailer
Publication Details: Written by Aakanksha Raghuvanshi  | Monday December 07, 2020, New Delhi

Title: England Tour Of South Africa Postponed Midway After Covid Outbreak
Description: South Africa vs England: The ODI series between South Africa and England was postponed on Monday to ensure "the mental and physical health and welfare of players from both teams," said ECB in a release.

Title: Rajinikanth Has Gurukripa, Is A Man Of His Word, Says His Elder Brother
Description: Ahead of launching his political party next month, Tamil superstar Rajinikanth paid a visit to his elder brother R Sathyanarayana Rao in Bengaluru, where he grew up.
Publication Details: Press Trust of India   | Monday December 07, 2020, Bengaluru

Title: India, Nepal Review Progress On Bilateral Trade And Economic Ties
Description: A meeting of the India-Nepal Inter-Governmental Committee (IGC) on Trade and Transit was held today, during which both sides reviewed the progress made on wide-ranging bilateral agenda including review of treaties of trade and transit, stated the Indian embassy.

Title: Green Peas Health Benefits: Do Not Miss These Impressive Benefits Of Matar This Winter
Description: Green peas are commonly available during the winter season. These can be added to your diet in several ways. Here are some notable health benefits of green peas you should not miss.
Publication Details: Written by Varsha Vats  | Monday December 07, 2020

Title: GoPro Hero 9 Black Review
Description: The GoPro Hero 9 Black features a new sensor that supports up to 5K video recording, a bigger battery, and new features. All of this comes with a higher price tag to match. We review it to see if it’s worth getting over the Hero 8 Black.

Title: IIT Roorkee Placements 2020: 632 Offers Made Till Day 6
Description: IIT Roorkee Placements 2020: By the end of day-six of the placement sessions, IIT Roorkee students had received 632 job offers from 147 recruiters.
Publication Details: Edited by Bhoomika Aggarwal  | Monday December 07, 2020

Title: Bumble, OKCupid Android Apps Plagued With an Old Flaw That Puts Millions of Users’ Data at Risk: Check Point
Description: Check Point notes that 13 percent of Google Play apps analysed by them in September used the Google Play Core library, and 8 percent of those apps continued to have a vulnerable version. Viber and Booking.com apps updated to patched versions after Check Point notified them about the vulnerability. Google acknowledged this bug in April and rated it an 8.8 out of 10 in severity.

Title: Bala Devi Becomes First Indian Woman Footballer To Score In Europe
Description: Bala Devi scored in the 85th minute to open her account for Rangers FC as they defeated Motherwell 9-0 on Sunday.

Title: IIIT Delhi To Start Centre of Excellence On Light Fidelity
Description: As part of the Indraprastha Institute of Information Technology’s (IIIT-Delhi) new project, the centre will design relevant courses on LiFi and facilitate capacity building by research collaborations.
Publication Details: Edited by Mridusmita Deka  | Monday December 07, 2020

Title: South Indian Recipes: How To Make Restaurant-Style Tomato-Onion Uttapam at Home
Description: Uttapam is a South Indian snack or breakfast that is made with rice batter on a griddle or tawa. It is often topped with chopped vegetables like onions, tomatoes, green chillies etc.

Title: BJP Using Sharad Pawar's Letter To "Confuse" People, Alleges NCP
Description: The BJP has been circulating letters of ex-Union agriculture minister Sharad Pawar randomly to "confuse" people after the Nationalist Congress Party declared support to farmers agitating against the Centres new farm laws, the NCP said on Monday.
Publication Details: Press Trust of India   | Monday December 07, 2020

Title: 47 Accused In Palghar Lynching Case Get Bail
Description: A Thane court on Monday granted bail to 47 people arrested in the Palghar mob lynching case. District Judge P P Jadhav ordered that the accused be released on a surety of Rs 15,000 each.
Publication Details: Press Trust of India   | Monday December 07, 2020, Thane

Title: Vivo Y52s With MediaTek Dimensity 720 SoC, Dual Rear Cameras Launched: Price, Specifications
Description: Vivo Y52s has been launched as the company’s newest mid-range 5G phone. The Vivo Y52s comes with a waterdrop-style display notch and dual rear cameras. The Vivo phone also carries the MediaTek Dimensity 720 SoC.
